## Deploying

### First Deployment

```bash
# Complete setup
kamal setup
```

### Subsequent Deployments

```bash
# Deploy updates
kamal deploy

# What happens:
# 1. Build Docker image locally
# 2. Push to registry
# 3. Pull image on servers
# 4. Run migrations
# 5. Start new containers
# 6. Health check
# 7. Switch traffic (zero-downtime)
# 8. Stop old containers
```

